author: cmlenz
msg: Improve error reporting when the test results cannot be retrieved:
- Always include the URL that had been used in the exception message
- If the status code is not 200, include the returned status code and message in the exception message
- Only include the body text of the response in the exception message if the response has a 200 status code, but the body content is not a valid <webresult> document
